node.text:
WIN! This week we are celebrating NAETUR’s 1 year anniversary @naetur Can’t believe it’s been a year already! I want to thank you all for your support by giving away 10 X €500,- shopping money 🖤

How to win: 

1. Follow @romeestrijd and @naetur 
2. Like this post
3. Tag 3 friends

Winners will receive a DM on Thursday, August 5.
